{"type":"message","id":"01ac9f75","parentId":"29153d30","timestamp":"2026-04-30T09:30:41.782Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:0c8b1d5b-b2fd-45d4-b346-517699a1e000 Morning Brief] Run the morning brief skill at ~/.openclaw/skills/morning-brief/SKILL.md. Follow it EXACTLY. Deliver all 7 sections to Telegram chat 8212808444 ONE SECTION AT A TIME. Sections: Header, Weather, Bible Verse, Emails (yesterday+today via Gmail API), Calendar (7 days), Reminders, Suggestions. Do NOT include X/Twitter. Send each section separately via message tool.\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 30th, 2026 - 5:30 AM (America/New_York) / 2026-04-30 09:30 UTC\n\nUse the message tool if you need to notify the user directly for the current chat. If you do not send directly, your final plain-text reply will be delivered automatically."}],"timestamp":1777541441778}}
{"type":"message","id":"17f6e18a","parentId":"01ac9f75","timestamp":"2026-04-30T09:32:35.854Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the morning brief skill file to understand how to run it exactly.","thinkingSignature":"951bbad413cc38d2e1162a84532608feb45aa2435a7b4a8cf1d6555afbc767e2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_viz4asv66865_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/skills/morning-brief/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":22682,"output":59,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22869,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777541441846,"responseId":"064254b060b0cca95400a1a668d260fd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0402a9e0","parentId":"17f6e18a","timestamp":"2026-04-30T09:32:35.886Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_viz4asv66865_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: morning-brief\ndescription: Run the daily morning brief for Bobby. Deliver via Telegram ONE SECTION AT A TIME to chat 8212808444.\n---\n\n# Morning Brief\n\nDeliver a complete morning brief to Telegram chat 8212808444. Send each section as a SEPARATE message, one at a time.\n\n**Output format — Section 1 (Header):**\n```\nGood morning, Bobby! ☀️\n\n[Day], [Month Date], Year\n\nHere's what we've got going on for today…\n```\n\n**Output format — Section 2 (Weather):**\n```\n🌤️ Knoxville Weather — [Date]\n\nNOW: [temp]° (feels like [feels]°)\nHIGH: [high]° | LOW: [low]°\nWIND: [wind] | HUMIDITY: [humidity]% | UV: [uv#] ([uv-level]) | RAIN: [rain]%\n\n⏰ HOUR BY HOUR:\n9AM: [temp]° [emoji]\n12PM: [temp]° [emoji]\n3PM: [temp]° [emoji]\n6PM: [temp]° [emoji]\n9PM: [temp]° [emoji]\n\n💡 VERDICT: [One sentence advice]\n```\n\nGet weather from: `python3 ~/.openclaw/skills/morning-brief/weather_script.py`\n\n**Output format — Section 3 (Bible Verse):**\n```\n📖 BIBLE VERSE OF THE DAY\n\n\"[verse_text]\"\n— [reference] ([version])\n\n💡 TODAY'S MOTIVATION: [2-3 sentences personalized to Bobby's day — reference his calendar, bills, reminders, or projects. Keep it motivational and specific.]\n```\n\nGet verse from: `openclaw browser open \"https://www.verseoftheday.com\"` then `openclaw browser snapshot`\n\n**Output format — Section 4 (Calendar):**\n```\n📅 YOUR WEEK ([date] — [date])\n\n[DAY] [M/D]:\n• [Event] — [Time]\nOR: • Free day!\n• ⚠️ Bills: [name] — [due date] — $[amount] [PAID/DUE]\n\n[Repeat for 7 days]\n\n---\n\n💡 BASED ON YOUR SCHEDULE:\n\n• [Bill reminder or schedule insight]\n```\n\nGet calendar from: `icalbuddy -c \"Family Calendar\" eventsToday+7`\n\nGet bills from: `python3 -c \"import json; bills=json.load(open('/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/bills_april_2026.json')); from datetime import datetime; today=datetime.now(); [print(f'• {b[\\\"name\\\"]} — {b[\\\"dueDate\\\"][5:]} — \\${b[\\\"amount\\\"]:.2f} [{\\\"✅ PAID\\\" if b.get(\\\"paid\\\") else \\\"⚠️ DUE\\\"}]') for b in bills if datetime.strptime(b['dueDate'],'%Y-%m-%d')<=today+__import__('datetime').timedelta(days=7)]\"`\n\n**Output format — Section 5 (Reminders):**\n```\n📝 REMINDERS\n\n• [Reminder]\n• [Reminder]\nOR: • None\n```\n\nGet from: `remindctl list Reminders` — show incomplete items only.\n\n**Output format — Section 6 (OpenClaw Update Check):**\nRun: `openclaw update status`\n\nIf an update is available:\n```\n🦞 OPENCLAW UPDATE AVAILABLE\n\nNew version: [version]\nChannel: [channel]\n\nDo you want me to update? (yes/no)\n```\nIf up to date: say NOTHING — skip this section entirely.\n\n**Output format — Section 7 (Suggestions):**\n```\n💡 WAYS I CAN HELP TODAY\n\n1. [Actionable suggestion — specific thing I can do for Bobby]\n2. [Another actionable suggestion]\n3. [Third actionable suggestion]\n4. [Fourth actionable suggestion]\n5. [Fifth actionable suggestion]\n6. [Sixth actionable suggestion]\n7. [Seventh actionable suggestion]\n```\n\nSuggestions must be things I can actively DO. Reference specific items from the brief.\n\n---\n\n## CRITICAL RULES\n- Send EACH section as a SEPARATE Telegram message\n- Send them ONE AT A TIME — complete section 1, send it, then do section 2\n- NEVER include \"SECTION X:\" labels in messages — only the formatted content\n- Use the message tool to send each section\n- Never guess data — use the commands provided\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777541555885}}
