ww.verseoftheday.com/en/05012026/\n    - img\n  - heading \"About\" [ref=e53] [level=3]\n  - paragraph:\n    - text: Verse of the day is currently read by over 1 million people each month. This ministry is supported by generous readers all over the world!\n    - link \"Donate to this Ministry\" [ref=e54]:\n      - /url: /support/\n      - img \"Donate to this Ministry\"\n  - paragraph:\n    - text: VerseoftheDay.com was started in 1998 by\n    - link \"Ben Steed\" [ref=e55]:\n      - /url: http://bensteed.com\n    - text: and became part of the\n    - link \"Heartlight\" [ref=e56]:\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org\n    - text: Network in 2000.\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"Heartlight Logo\" [ref=e57]:\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org\n      - img \"Heartlight Logo\"\n  - heading \"More Daily Devos:\" [ref=e58] [level=3]\n  - heading \"Passion for Praise\" [ref=e59] [level=4]:\n    - link \"Passion for Praise\" [ref=e60]:\n      - /url: http://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/passionforpraise.cgi\n  - text: A daily passage of Scripture emphasizing praise to our God.\n  - link \"Read Today's 'Passion for Praise' Devotional\" [ref=e61]:\n    - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/passionforpraise.cgi?day=20260430\n    - img \"Read Today's 'Passion for Praise' Devotional\"\n  - text: \"'How Great You Are!' (2 Sa. 7:22)\"\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"\\\" [ref=e62]How great you are, O Sovereign Lord! There is none like you.\\\"\":\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/passionforpraise.cgi?day=20260430\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"Subscribe to Passion for Praise\" [ref=e63]:\n      - /url: https://www.verseoftheday.com/subscribe.php?lang=pfp&KeepThis=true&TB_iframe=true&height=300&width=445\n      - img\n      - text: Subscribe to Passion for Praise\n  - heading \"Praying with Paul\" [ref=e64] [level=4]:\n    - link \"Praying with Paul\" [ref=e65]:\n      - /url: http://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/praying_paul/pwp.pl\n  - text: Features the apostle Paul's writings turned into daily, powerful prayers.\n  - link \"Read Today's 'Praying with Paul' Devotional\" [ref=e66]:\n    - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/praying_paul/pwp.pl?120\n    - img \"Read Today's 'Praying with Paul' Devotional\"\n  - text: \"'Speaking Truth' (1 Co. 14:13-25)\"\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"\\\" [ref=e67] [nth=1]Dear Father, God of intelligibility and peace, Let our praying, singing, and preaching be aimed at informing the minds and spirits of others, that...\\\"\":\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/cgi-shl/praying_paul/pwp.pl?120\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"Subscribe to Praying with Paul\" [ref=e68]:\n      - /url: https://www.verseoftheday.com/subscribe.php?lang=pwp&KeepThis=true&TB_iframe=true&height=300&width=445\n      - img\n      - text: Subscribe to Praying with Paul\n  - heading \"Spiritual Warfare\" [ref=e69] [level=4]:\n    - link \"Spiritual Warfare\" [ref=e70]:\n      - /url: http://www.heartlight.org/spiritualwarfare/\n  - text: A daily devotional about God's power for our battles.\n  - link \"Read Today's 'Spiritual Warfare' Devotional\" [ref=e71]:\n    - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/spiritualwarfare/en/0430/\n    - img \"Read Today's 'Spiritual Warfare' Devotional\"\n  - text: \"'A Fool and His Earthly Wealth' (Lk. 12:20-21)\"\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"\\\" [ref=e72] [nth=2]But God said to him, 'You fool! You will die this very night. Then who will get everything you worked for?' Yes, a person is a fool to store up...\\\"\":\n      - /url: https://www.heartlight.org/spiritualwarfare/en/0430/\n  - paragraph:\n    - link \"Subscribe to Spiritual Warfare\" [ref=e73]:\n      - /url: https://www.verseoftheday.com/subscribe.php?lang=sw&KeepThis=true&TB_iframe=true&height=300&width=445\n      - img\n      - text: Subscribe to Spiritual Warfare\n  - heading \"Translations\" [ref=e74] [level=3]\n  - list:\n    - listitem:\n      - link \"English\" [ref=e75]:\n        - /url: /en/\n    - listitem: