{"type":"message","id":"4c0687a9","parentId":"98fed7ca","timestamp":"2026-04-30T09:34:03.807Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I got emails from the mission control server. Now I also need today's emails. Let me fetch those too. The API returned emails - let me also get today's ones.\n\nActually, looking at the API, it seems to return recent emails already (yesterday and today). Let me now also check if there's a way to get emails from today (April 30). Let me query the mission control API for today's emails too.\n\nLet me now compile all the data and start sending sections.\n\nFirst, let me filter the important emails (not promotions) for the email section.\n\nLooking at the emails, the important non-promotional ones from yesterday (Apr 29) are:\n- ngrok news (unread) - could be important\n\n\n- SoundCloud weekly (unread) - less important\n- Indeed job alert (unread) - could be relevant\n- Capital One creditwise (unread) - less critical\n- ZipRecruiter job matches (unread) - potentially important\n- iHeart daily (unread) - entertainment\n- ZipRecruiter diag partners (unread) - job related\n- Citizens Pay statement (unread) - financial\n- PetScreening (unread) - could be important\n- TikTok notifications (unread) - social\n- Xfinity refund (unread) - financial, appears important\n- PetScreening non-compliant (unread) - potentially significant\n- TikTok social (unread) - less critical\n- USPS Informed Delivery (unread) - could be important\n\nNow I need to figure out how to fetch today's emails since the current API call only returned yesterday's messages. Let me check what other endpoints the mission control server exposes so I can get today's emails as well.","thinkingSignature":"9f7697e1c0e65025867d8f485fb0d5939dbb4c08fe263e6ae017afcea458a3ee"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lsay83bt9jrc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/emails/today 2>/dev/null | head -100 || curl -s http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/calendar 2>/dev/null | head -100 || echo \"Endpoints not available\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2692,"output":443,"cacheRead":31584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34719,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777541625828,"responseId":"064254f990c073bf5c115e26efd2f827"}}
