{"type":"message","id":"b12c7aee","parentId":"1fd728f0","timestamp":"2026-04-30T09:34:49.499Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now Section 3: Bible Verse","thinkingSignature":"502f1ddea48a41907530906552127242ee78018a17e961d4c124042118d70cc9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_a13osis7d78u_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"📖 BIBLE VERSE OF THE DAY\n\n\"Speaking the truth in love, we will in all things grow up into him who is the Head, that is, Christ.\"\n— Ephesians 4:15 (NIV)\n\n💡 TODAY'S MOTIVATION: Truth and love aren't opposites — they go together. Today you've got meetings on the calendar and bills to track, but remember: how you communicate matters just as much as what you communicate. Speak clearly, stay kind, and you'll get further than you would trying to win arguments. Also — with all the moving pieces this week (KUB, apartments, apartment hunting), cut yourself some slack. You're doing a lot. That's exactly what \"growing up into Christ\" looks like in real life: showing up, doing the work, and doing it with love.","target":"8212808444"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":253,"output":219,"cacheRead":37088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37560,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777541685131,"responseId":"06425535f7a455cea729fc4016d4da7e"}}
