{"type":"message","id":"893d5cfb","parentId":"8381ca88","timestamp":"2026-04-30T09:34:57.289Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now Section 4 - Calendar. Let me format the calendar events properly. I have:\n- Apple Card - $64.00 today at 9:00-9:30 AM\n- Affirm Marriott - $129.59 day after tomorrow at 9:00-9:30 AM\n- Cinco de Mayo - May 5\n- Pay KUB - May 7\n\nAnd bills from the bills.json:\n- Capital One Quicksilver - 04-27 - $96.00 ⚠️ DUE (already past due)\n- Apple Card Payment - 04-30 - $64.00 ⚠️ DUE (today)\n\n\n- I'll compile the full 7-day calendar from today, April 30 through May 6, with both the calendar events and any bills that fall within that window.","thinkingSignature":"26fde53cd597f046c61ee239f59cc36516247947cb5c99bc19446483269817c4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yg0b9fd558lm_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"📅 YOUR WEEK (Apr 30 — May 6)\n\nTHURSDAY Apr 30:\n• Apple Card ($64) — today at 9:00 AM ⚠️ DUE\n\nFRIDAY May 1:\n• Free day!\n\nSATURDAY May 2:\n• Free day!\n\nSUNDAY May 3:\n• Free day!\n\nMONDAY May 4:\n• Free day!\n\nTUESDAY May 5:\n• Free day!\n• ⚠️ Bills: Capital One Quicksilver ($96.00) — past due since Apr 27\n\nWEDNESDAY May 6:\n• Free day!\n\n---\n\n💡 BASED ON YOUR SCHEDULE:\n\n• Apple Card payment ($64) is due TODAY — consider paying it now before the morning meeting\n• Capital One Quicksilver ($96) is past due since Apr 27 — prioritize this one this week\n• Affirm Marriott ($129.59) is due May 2 — that's the day after tomorrow\n• KUB payment is coming up May 7 — plan for that this week too","target":"8212808444"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":279,"output":432,"cacheRead":37312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38023,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777541689946,"responseId":"06425539bbf163a480337b94b44f8bb2"}}
